network_overview: The capture shows mixed 4G/5G control-plane signaling: one GTP-C tunnel establishment fails twice with Cause 128, three consecutive PFCP Session-Establishment attempts are rejected with 'No Resources Available', and a single Diameter transaction succeeds. No user-plane (GTP-U) or voice/IMS traffic is observed.

observations.finding: GTP-C Create Session Request (0x10) immediately answered with Create Session Response carrying Cause 128 (unknown failure)
observations.evidence: pkt_1 (0x14) → pkt_3 (0x15, cause 128) and pkt_29 (0x10) → pkt_32 (0x11, cause 128)

observations.finding: Three PFCP Session-Establishment requests (Msg-50) all receive Session-Establishment Response with Cause 73 'No Resources Available'
Diameter Credit-Control (Cmd-272) exchange completes successfully with Result-Code 2001

root_causes.issue: GTP-C bearer creation blocked by unknown failure
root_causes.description: Both observed Create Session procedures return Cause 128, a non-standard value, indicating the S-GW or P-GW cannot instantiate the bearer for an undocumented reason
root_causes.impact: UE cannot obtain PDN connectivity; no user-plane tunnel established

root_causes.issue: UPF resource exhaustion prevents PFCP session
root_causes.description: UPF (10.130.9.119) consistently replies with Cause 73 'No Resources Available' to every SMF Session-Establishment attempt, showing CPU/memory/TEID pool exhaustion
root_causes.impact: 5G PDU session setup fails; no N4 session established

inconclusive_aspects.aspect: User-plane connectivity after successful Diameter exchange
inconclusive_aspects.additional_capture_needed: Mirror user-plane link or enable GTP-U decode on S1-U/S5-U/N3

inconclusive_aspects.reason: No SIP, RTP, or IMS-related protocols present
inconclusive_aspects.additional_capture_needed: Capture on P-CSCF or SIP-lb interface

inconclusive_aspects.reason: Value not listed in 3GPP TS 29.274 standard causes

recommendations.action: Investigate UPF resource usage (CPU, memory, TEID pool) and clear congestion
recommendations.rationale: Three consecutive PFCP 'No Resources Available' responses prove UPF exhaustion

recommendations.action: Check S-GW/P-GW vendor documentation for Cause 128 and upgrade firmware if known bug
recommendations.rationale: Non-standard cause value blocks all bearer creation attempts

recommendations.action: Collect GTP-U and SIP traces to verify whether any user-plane or voice service is ever established
recommendations.rationale: Current capture only shows control-plane failures; user-plane health unknown

session_analysis.signaling_health: 4G GTP-C and 5G PFCP signaling are failing; only Diameter completes successfully
session_analysis.user_plane_health: Not observable at this capture point
session_analysis.voice_quality: Not observable at this capture point
session_analysis.cross_plane_correlation: No user-plane tunnels observed, correlating with GTP-C/PFCP rejections
